= Introduction =
This wiki should become the greatest resource helping you to find the most
productive workflows fast.

See [[topic/this-wiki-design-goals]]

contributing:
[[topic/contributing-to-this-wiki]]
[[topic/github]]

= how to get help about vim =
* :help (use vim's builtin help
* try google
* [[topic/vim-irc-on-freenode]]
* mailingilst {{http://www.vim.org/community.php}}


If installing git is too much pain you can also register at github and file a bug report describing
what you'd change on this wiki: [[http://github.com/MarcWeber/vim-git-wiki/issues|bug tracker]]

